 Khafi & Gedoni Ekpata Ex Big Brother Naija housemates Khafi Kareem and Gedoni Ekpata ties the knot. Khafi and Gedoni got engaged on Thursday, December 26, 2020 and made it official at the Ikoyi Marriage Registry on, Thursday, September 24, 2020. Khafi made the announcement of their wedding exactly a year after their engagement on her Instagram page View this post on Instagram A post shared by Khafi Kareem (A Cup Of Khafi) (@acupofkhafi) Congratulations to the newly weds Mr & Mrs Ekpata